submissions.text: Hello its me Golly , I just wanna to say exactly this day ,one year ago I showed you guys my art for the first time and the response was so great I keep showing and showing .Now ,a year have gone by and it was such a wild ride for me , thanks to you guys I managed to get my own pc for the first time in my life and Vr and a table and a drawing tablet, my life just changed after that . From the bottom of my heart I want to say thank you so much and I love everyone,all the love and support I appreciate all of it , I hope my silly drawings repay some of it . I hope your (Rob) community keep growing and have even more beautiful memories in the future. Thank you for changing this lil rice farmer life and please do have a lovely day ~Golly ( ps welcome back Rob, we all missed you a lot ,now back to work lump head)

submissions.author: nonautologous#4523
submissions.text: The remnants of wars and countries long forgotten has left humanity hostile and cold as the very space they inhabit. In the year 73 C.E, the ruins of an abandoned colony begins to drift towards earth. The battleship Minerva has been ordered to destroy the descending wreckage and prevent it from crashing into the planet below, however rogue Soldiers have thwarted their attempt, decimating the allied earth union and their forces on the surface below. from the fallen wreckage, war erupts between the factions with the three travelers caught in the crossfire. Forced to choose sides, will the anachronistic travelers meet upon the battle field, the Seeds of their Destiny spilled like Iron Blood upon the Orphaned planet at the Origin of this AGE of chaos? https://imgur.com/a/YYYTJkA

Thus the Power Puff Bunny Girls were born!
